cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with visual localization for autonomous driving, which involves computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories. The paper also deals with autonomous driving, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category.
